{"tid":213971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望有人收留佢地","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T13:08:21.000Z","uid":20584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62bd9c3fb3a3b6cccc54c480aa1251a569e27bc8","tid":213971,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/205729_a3bd828be9241471901dad8e463b5d7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F205729_a3bd828be9241471901dad8e463b5d7d.jpg&h=49235a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0V6d4mf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0V6d4mf.jpg&h=96ae8313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陪左我幾年，因為要換床唔夠位先唔捨得要扔，如果有人想要請搵我。雖然係二手野，但係我好錫佢地，算幾乾淨，想要可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45245a82a196c900b413799c9bec34726657f85a","tid":213971,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"可以留低tg"},{"pid":"f578a77aa1da2e285d3cce2fe743a500ac52f437","tid":213971,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aa9e9e00d749c0f367940ab0fe1d3502fdf56d6","tid":213971,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"無攬啊 佢地訓上面 我訓下面 所以好乾淨"},{"pid":"ca859b0469cee0775be56783bbd074b691d892ee","tid":213971,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主隻史納莎邊到買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359a6bed8fab4c253754d64bac3f804bc512aac2","tid":213971,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下樓主隻史納莎邊到買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個唔係好清楚啊 唔好意思 因為係朋友生日送 <br />\n<br />\n其實唔洗擔心咁多會臭會舊既問題 因為平時佢地只係訓上格床，我得閒先會攬一攬佢地<br />\n<br />\n而家只係想有人中意既話可以收留佢地。"},{"pid":"a89076f6c572b0241a711e600d82cd7edf6f0647","tid":213971,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"你唔好唔要佢地啦"},{"pid":"dc502d34e3ae054272e91a90e895931a0a4505ac","tid":213971,"uid":2917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:18:30.000Z","msg":"隻史納莎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 我諗起hello kitty頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df66a586ea7fe49c8cffaa25ba3ea698fa0b2275","tid":213971,"uid":54095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"收留ON 金牌蛋白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdbce86c8be7bed136143066e0768e06ece92df","tid":213971,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"好少史納莎公仔咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以郵寄俾我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6429d05640a224b14432f89972316afed56d69d","tid":213971,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好少史納莎公仔咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以郵寄俾我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以啊，但係郵費share返你介唔介意？"},{"pid":"6afd62f10385fec96d1d8c9ecae9afe8fffda975","tid":2